    "Cs represent the intensities of the emerging spectrum.",
    "The present study introduces a novel feature ensembler.",
    "The ensembler in question incorporates a collection of features derived from various feature extraction methods.",
    "The data frame contains 288 elements extracted from each audio file.",
    "In our approach, we first used the Standard Scaler, a standard normalization technique, to normalize the features in our dataset."
